(define/contract (min-operations nums k)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let* ([xor-all (apply bitwise-xor nums)]
         [desired-xor (bitwise-xor xor-all k)]
         [max-bit (integer-length (apply max (cons k nums)))]
         [flip-counts (make-vector max-bit 0)])
    (for-each (lambda (num)
                (let* ([diff (bitwise-xor num k)]
                       [diff-bits (for/list ([i (in-range max-bit)])
                                    (bitwise-bit-set? diff i))])
                  (for ([i (in-range max-bit)])
                    (when (list-ref diff-bits i)
                      (vector-set! flip-counts i (+ 1 (vector-ref flip-counts i)))))))
              nums)
    (let* ([flips-required (map (lambda (i)
                                  (if (bitwise-bit-set? desired-xor i)
                                      (vector-ref flip-counts i)
                                      (- (length nums) (vector-ref flip-counts i))))
                                (build-list max-bit values))]
           [min-flips (apply min flips-required)])
      (if (zero? desired-xor) 0 min-flips))))
